sourcesContent:
const timelineElements = [
  {
    id: 0,
    title: "Bachelor of Computer Engineering",
    location: "Polytechnique Montréal, Canada",
    description:
      "As I progress in my studies, I eagerly anticipate discovering my"
      +"true passion within this dynamic field. Whether it's hardware,"
      + "software, robotics, telecommunications, medical technologies,"
      +"or aerospace, I am determined to make a meaningful impact on the future of technology."
      +"With 62 credits completed out of 120 and an excellent academic record (GPA 3.56/4.00)," 
      +"I embrace the challenges and excitement of the journey ahead with enthusiasm and dedication.",
    date: "August 2021 - August 2025",
  },
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Preparatory Year",
    location: "Polytechnique Montréal, Canada",
    description:
     "During the preparatory year, I engaged in a comprehensive training program"
     +"centered around fundamental disciplines like mathematics, physics, chemistry,"
     +"and computer science, complemented by communication skills. This interdisciplinary"
     +"approach has allowed me to build a strong foundation in essential sciences while "
     +"fostering effective communication abilities.",
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Professional Master of Architecture",
    location: "University of Constantine, Algeria",
    description: " During my Professional Master of Architecture program, "
    +"I immersed myself in a comprehensive and specialized curriculum, refining"
    +"my skills in architectural design, project management, and sustainable practices. "
    +"This transformative experience has equipped me with the expertise and creative "
    +"vision needed to shape innovative and environmentally conscious spaces. "
    +"As I now step into the professional world, I am eager to contribute my passion "
    +"for architecture and make a positive impact on the built environment.",
    date: "September 2009 - August 2014",
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    title: "French Baccalaureate major in science",
    location: "Mila, Algeria",
    description: "Strengthened scientific knowledge, honed analytical skills. Ready for further studies or professional opportunities in the field.",
    date: "September 2006 - August 2009",
  },
];

export default timelineElements;
